cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite the accompanying paper."
title: "SAGE"
abstract: >
  A guardrailed LLM tutor that scaffolds self-regulated learning for adult
  learners. It wraps a commercial LLM with interface-level scaffolds (plan,
  paraphrase, attempt) and an online counterfactual fairness audit across age,
  language dominance, prior education, and digital-fluency markers.
